title: Actress rocks zero underwear for eye-popping see-through dress
text:
Getty NAKED AMBITION: The actress left her underwear at home for her daring look 
The Westworld actress stunned guests at the Vanity Fair and L'Oreal Paris Toast to Young Hollywood party this week when she rocked up in a daring look. 
Wearing a chic floor-length number, Angela looked conservative from the front, but that all changed when she turned to the side. 
Lined with two sheer panels, the dress left nothing to the imagination as every inch of the actress' skin was on display. Celebrity nip slips, sideboobs & underboobs Friday, 3rd February 2017 They may be rich and famous, but these celebrities aren't immune from flashing the flesh in our ultimate celebrity nip slips, sideboobs, underboobs and now gapboobs gallery. 1 / 220 Charlotte Dawson and Ela Rose have both suffered major nipple slips 
Splash WHO NEEDS UNDERWEAR? Angela wasn't afraid to flash the flesh 
Taking the flesh-flashing look to the extreme, Angela left her bra and knickers at home. 
Because underwear is just so last season, right? 
With a touch of side boob on show, the 33-year-old no doubt left onlookers with their jaws on the floor. Related videos
